Usage: init_ml [-help] [-comment <string>] [-flow_phase <string>]
               [-name <string>] -prefix <string> [-scenario <string>]

-help                # Prints out the command usage
-comment <string>    # comment (string, optional)
-flow_phase <string> # flow phase (string, optional)
-name <string>       # design name (string, optional)
-prefix <string>     # Prefix for output files (string, required)
-scenario <string>   # scenario (string, optional)